snippet.title: Attack on Titan: Rogue Titan VS Armored Titan (Unofficial version)

localized.description:
The Rogue Titan squares off against The Armored Titan in this edited fan made Clash of the Titans video!

No, this isn't the "real" thing for those that are caught up with the Manga.  Yes its fake DUH, that's the point.  It's edited clips put together. Leaving comments saying that the outcome of this "fight" isn't the same as in the Manga, makes you a fucking idiot.

Last but definitely not least, A BIG THANK YOU for all that liked this video, you guys are awesome!! And its what keeps me going in making videos like these.

Edited with Sony Vegas Pro 12.
